{"root":{"data":{"id":"djvbx91ttbs0","created":1783731156895,"text":"双穿世界","expandState":"expand","font-size":32,"color":"#ff0000"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvbxm9qab40","created":1783731185671,"text":"梦魇世界","expandState":"expand","layout":null,"font-size":24,"color":"#00b0f0"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmk998fxs0","created":1783761170818,"text":"世界信息","layout":null,"font-size":16,"font-weight":"bold"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmmssjgeg0","created":1783761370072,"text":"世界信息","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvmr9hqlrc0","created":1783761719881,"text":"2012年,很多人在无意中觉醒了精神异能","priority":1,"layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvndtdbfog0","created":1783763487161,"text":"现在是2016年,主角的母亲发现自己觉醒了精神异能","priority":2},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvneh7s3bs0","created":1783763539069,"text":"分支主题"},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmn9gzfog0","created":1783761406379,"text":"政府结构","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmnn2i4rc0","created":1783761435978,"text":"针对超能力者态度","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmi8wc7lk0","created":1783761013309,"text":"李其乐","layout":null,"font-weight":"bold","font-size":16,"expandState":"expand"},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvml701ryo0","created":1783761244273,"text":"家庭信息","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvms9ddn340","created":1783761797981,"text":"父亲:李雅军,山阳玻璃厂钳工班班长","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmu75ario0","created":1783761949868,"text":"母亲:郭香兰,山阳玻璃厂流水线打包女工","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvmwwx5cyo0","created":1783762162700,"text":"大伯:李雅国,悦客饭馆","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn0l23zt40","created":1783762450335,"text":"堂姐:李其凤,大伯女儿,同省一本大学生,临近毕业","layout":null},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djvn1m1ghmg0","created":1783762530836,"text":"堂哥:李其麟,大伯儿子,同一学校同一届高中生","layout":null},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djvmlx13pvc0","created":1783761300933,"text":"身份背景","layout":null},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djvn2gj1k1s0","created":1783762597203,"